---
title: Global Configurations
label: Configuration
---

All available Fox Tail UI configuration options.

| Name                                          | Description                                            | Default                      |
|-----------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------|
| config.fox\_tail.classname\_merger            | Used to merge Tailwind Classes safely.                 | FoxTail::ClassnameMerger.new |
| config.fox\_tail.stimulus\_merger             | Used to merge Stimulus HTML element attributes.        | FoxTail::StimulusMerger.new  |
| config.fox\_tail.use\_stimulus                | Use stimulus controllers for interactive components.   | true                         |
| config.fox\_tail.raise\_on\_asset\_not\_found | Raise an error when embedding assets into the HTML.    | true                         |
| config.fox\_tail.color\_theme                 | Default options for the `FoxFail::ColorThemeComponent` | {}                           |
